# ===== Dominio: www -> sin www y HTTP -> HTTPS =====
https://www.vivaspeak.com/*  https://vivaspeak.com/:splat  301!
http://www.vivaspeak.com/*   https://vivaspeak.com/:splat  301!
http://vivaspeak.com/*       https://vivaspeak.com/:splat  301!

